<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    
    header {
        color: #333;
        padding: 40px 0;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ff385c;
    }
    
    h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase; 
        font-weight: bold; 
    }
    
    main {
        max-width: 100%; 
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    section {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    h2 {
        color:#ff385c; 
        border-bottom: 2px solid #00CFFF;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        position: relative; 
    }
    
    h2::after {
        content: ''; 
        display: block;
        width: 50px; 
        height: 3px;
        background-color: #00CFFF; 
        margin-top: 5px; 
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
        display: flex; 
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px; 
    }
    
    .content-wrapper img {
        width: 50%; 
        height: auto; 
        border-radius: 12px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05); 
    }
    
    .text-content {
        width: 50%; 
        padding-left: 7px; 
    }
    .intro p,
    .mission p,
    .story p,
    .join-us p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    
   
    .intro p,
    .mission p,
    .story p,
    .join-us p {
        color: #333; 
        line-height: 1.8; 
    }
    
   
    .intro p,
    .mission p,
    .story p,
    .join-us p {
       text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    
    
    .offerings ul,
    .values ul {
       list-style-type: none; 
       padding-left: 0; 
    }
    
    .offerings li,
    .values li {
       background-color: #e7f3ff;
       border-left: 5px solid #007BFF;
       padding: 10px; 
       margin-bottom: 10px; 
       transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
       position: relative;
    }
   
    .offerings li:hover,
    .values li:hover {
       background-color: #d1e7fd; 
       box-shadow: inset 2px 2px 5px rgba(255,255,255,0.6), inset -5px -5px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
</style>

<header>
    <h1>About Us</h1>
</header>

<main>
    <section class="intro">
        <div class="content-wrapper" style="text-align: justify;">
            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/509553708/photo/tropical-modern-villa-exterior.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=rMmOmihiXHl6htuhYVzbfPdKAawYHFuNMhD32A0sWUg=" alt="Travel Experience">
            <div class="text-content">
                <p style="max-width: 37rem; margin-left: 2rem">Welcome to <strong style="color: rgb(255, 68, 0);">Wanderlust</strong>, where we believe in creating memorable travel experiences through unique accommodations. Our platform connects travelers with local hosts, offering a diverse range of properties that cater to every taste and budget.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <div class="content-wrapper" style="text-align: justify;">
            <div class="text-content">
                <p style="max-width: 37rem; margin-right: 2rem">At <strong style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Wanderlust</strong>, our mission is to transform the way people travel by providing a peer-to-peer marketplace that allows guests to find authentic stays while enabling hosts to share their spaces with the world. We aim to foster community connections and promote local cultures through personalized travel experiences.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/06/13/33/21/360_F_613332177_rdl36d2CnlqC1tqGQE3CizEJdu9G2Ltj.jpg" alt="Our Mission Image" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="values">
        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Trust:</strong> We strive to create a safe environment for both guests and hosts. Our verification processes and review systems ensure that every listing meets our quality standards.</li>
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We are committed to clear communication regarding fees, policies, and expectations, helping users make informed decisions.</li>
            <li><strong>Sustainability:</strong> We support eco-friendly practices and encourage our community to be mindful of their environmental impact while traveling.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="offerings">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Diverse Listings:</strong> From cozy apartments in bustling cities to serene cabins in nature, our platform features a wide variety of properties to suit every traveler’s needs.</li>
            <li><strong>User-Friendly Experience:</strong> We prioritize ease of use, allowing guests to search, book, and communicate with hosts effortlessly.</li>
            <li><strong>Community Focus:</strong> We believe in the power of community. Our platform encourages hosts to share their local insights, helping guests discover hidden gems during their travels.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="join-us">
        <h2>Join Us</h2>
        <p>Whether you’re looking for your next adventure or hoping to share your space with travelers from around the globe, <strong style="color: rgb(255, 68, 0);">Wanderlust</strong> is here to facilitate those connections. Join us today and become part of our growing community!</p>
        <p>For any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out through our Contact Us page.
        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; font-size: larger">Thank you for choosing <strong style="color: rgb(255, 68, 0);">Wanderlust</strong>—we can’t wait to help you create unforgettable memories!</p></p>    
    </section>
</main>
